The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Sunday, March 11, 2007

 Biz buzz

 Be a part of Xaviers Management Convention 2007 on Resurgent Bengal Challenges and Opportunities, presented by The Telegraph, on the St Xaviers College campus, 8.30 am.

 Talking heads

 Attend All India Optometric Conference, presented in association with The Telegraph, at Sisir Mancha, 10 am.

 Cricket Cup

 McDowells No. 1 presents The Telegraph Cup Cricket for Merchants, in association with Sterling Resorts, at Calcutta Cricket amp; Football Club, 5.30 pm.

 On a high 

 Watch mountaineering and adventure film shows, organised by South Calcutta Trekkers Association, at Asutosh Birth Centenary Hall, Indian Museum, 2.30 pm to 9 pm.

 Showstopper

 Dont miss the North East Crafts Fair at Bidhannagar Municipal Sports Complex, 11 am to 8 pm.

 Browse through portraits by PC Banerjee at Palladian Lounge, Bengal Chamber of Commerce and Industry, 10 am to 7 pm.

 Smooth moves

 Enjoy Odissi Sandhya, presented by Odissi Ashram, at EZCC, 6 pm.




